# Orbital Health - Cursor Rules

## PRE-SUBMISSION RULE
Before ANY task that touches auth, IAP, 
app.json, or PrivacyInfo — automatically 
run the checklist in .cursor/skills/app-store-submission.md
and report results before making changes.

## SILENT FAILURE RULE  
Never allow .catch(() => {}) anywhere in 
auth or IAP flows. Every catch must either:
- Show Alert.alert to user, OR
- Log with __DEV__ guard only

## FORBIDDEN TERMS RULE
Before every build touching user-visible strings,
run: grep -r "diagnosis\|treatment\|therapy\|medical device\|HIPAA\|CPT\|FDA" app/ components/
Zero tolerance. Fix before proceeding.

## PRIVACYINFO RULE
ios/Orbital/PrivacyInfo.xcprivacy must never 
be deleted. If git status shows it as deleted,
restore immediately before any other work.

## BUILD NUMBER RULE
Before every eas build, confirm buildNumber 
in app.json is higher than last submitted build.
Last submitted (update when you ship): 79 (EAS production auto-increment may bump app.json during build).
Next build must be higher than that.

## SENTRY XCODE RULE
Before eas iOS build: ensure Upload Debug Symbols to Sentry in
ios/Orbital.xcodeproj/project.pbxproj does NOT use a hardcoded absolute path
to sentry-xcode-debug-files.sh (breaks on EAS: /Users/expo/workingdir/build).
Use NODE_BINARY + require.resolve('@sentry/react-native/...') after sourcing
.xcode.env — same pattern as Bundle React Native + sentry-xcode.sh.

## EAS CACHE RULE
eas.json production: do not use custom cache.paths that include ios/Pods
(Save cache phase can fail after a successful archive). If Save cache errors,
use EAS_USE_CACHE=0 in production env and remove the custom cache block.

## APP ICON RULE
app.json expo.plugins: ./plugins/withAppIcon must stay FIRST. iOS AppIcon.appiconset
must use one universal 1024 entry (idiom universal, platform ios). See
docs/APP_STORE_PREFLIGHT.md §12.

## APP STORE SCREENSHOTS RULE
Use Maestro + bundle exec fastlane screenshots → fastlane/screenshots/en-US/,
then bundle exec fastlane deliver_screenshots (not raw fastlane snapshot unless
UITests exist). ASC API key must be App Manager for screenshot upload.
See docs/APP_STORE_PREFLIGHT.md §13.

## Stack
- Expo SDK 54, Reanimated 4.1.x, worklets 0.5.1, router v6
- @shopify/react-native-skia for orb shader
- TypeScript strict mode
- Supabase backend

## Conventions
- Be concise. No filler.
- Default to TypeScript. No JavaScript files.
- Functional components with hooks. No class components.
- All JS calls from worklets must use runOnJS
- Never add dependencies without asking first
- Use ReturnType<typeof setTimeout> for timer types
- Gate console.log behind __DEV__
- Run npx tsc --noEmit after every code change

## Commit messages
type: description — fix:, feat:, chore:

## Shortcuts
- "ship it" → submit skill
- "check it" → preflight skill
- "clean it" → refactor skill on file being viewed

## Forbidden terms in user-visible strings
diagnosis, treatment, therapy, medical device, HIPAA, CPT, FDA

## Git
- Never create branches. Commit to current branch.
- Never push without being told.
- Never force push.
